        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么紧绷着脸？在她睡着时和你说这些，让你有负罪感了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我反手抓住她勾着我鬓角的手指，摇了摇头，将手指贴到她的嘴唇上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在搞清楚对方的真正目的前，为了我，先装会傻吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "艾尔莎",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了，我？",
